  "title": "Senior Cyber Security Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Cyber Security Specialist</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>Architect, design, review and implement cyber security resilient in our product and projects. You are familiar with cloud security architectures and solutions, making sure the companies can operate in a safe, secure environment.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Responsible in managing CyberSecurity VAPT, Vulnerability Assessment, Risk Management and Testing.</li><li>Involved in Security test,configuration and installation of the security test preparation, setting-up of testing environment, configuration and installation of the security testing tools.</li><li>Strong in Cloud Azure Infrastructure</li><li>Conduct Microsoft Cloud Infrastructure Vulnerability Assessment and Penetration Testing Find pinpoint the vulnerabilities of the assess target system / application</li><li>Experience in handling Security Compliance, Assessment, Audit, Regulations and Governance.</li><li><strong>Knowledge and technical hands-on experience with Microsoft Azure, Entra ID and Microsoft 365 is a must</strong></li><li><strong>Strong experience in Cloud Azure Infrastructure Design and Azure and Cloud Security infrastructure is required.</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Skills Required</strong></u></p><ul><li>Strong in hands on technical Microsoft Cloud Azure, Microsoft 365 and Cloud Security.</li><li>Good in Cloud Infrastructure Architect and Stakeholder Management.</li><li>Technically incline in CyberSecurity, Cloud, Risk and Vulnerabilities.</li><li>Implement and maintain security policies and procedures to protect the organization’s IT assets.</li><li>Handle Customer’s ICT and cybersecurity incident response plan through ongoing security reviews and audits.</li><li>Strong in vulnerability scanning and security assessments of applications, including client/server software and mobile apps, to be deployed in corporate networks.</li><li><strong>Vulnerability Management, CA Privilege Access Management, CyberArk, GCSOC (Government Cyber Security Operations Center).</strong></li><li> Possess CyberSecurity certifications.</li><li>Maintain adherence to ISO 27001 certification and improve on NIST Gap Assessment.</li><li>Only Singaporean!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
